Description:
Annotation on the envelope: "Rubens XXII Landsknechte"

- Photocopies of reproductions of the 'Marauding Soldiers'
- Correspondence with the Kunsthistorisches Museum of Vienna (dated 1943), with the Bayerischen Staatsgemäldesammlungen of Munich (dated 1943) and with F. J. Sanchez Cantón (dated 1943)
- Draft text "XXII. Landsknechte"
- Extracts from different publications and notes
